        <div class="product-card__image">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="kb-col kb-col--50 product-card__right">
        <p class="product-card__description">
          Designer Karim Rashid continues to put his signature spin on all genres of design through various collaborations with top-notch companies. Another one to add to the win column is his work with Italian manufacturer Chateau d'Ax.
        </p>
        <div class="product-card__availability">
          <p class="product-card__text">
            In stock.
            <a class="kb-link">
              Buy Extended Warranty
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card__ratings">
          <ul class="kb-lists">
            <li class="kb-lists__item">
              <i class="material-icons active">star</i>
            </li>
            <li class="kb-lists__item">
              <i class="material-icons active">star</i>
            </li>
            <li class="kb-lists__item">
              <i class="material-icons active">star</i>
            </li>
            <li class="kb-lists__item">
              <i class="material-icons active">star</i>
            </li>
            <li class="kb-lists__item">
              <i class="material-icons">star</i>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <span class="product-card__review">
            (4.67 - 172 reviews)
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card__quantity">
          <span class="kb-card__support-text">
            Quantity
          </span>
          <div class="kb-carousel">
            <button class="kb-carousel__left">
              <i class="material-icons">keyboard_arrow_left</i>
            </button>
            <span class="kb-carousel__content">
              03
            </span>
            <button class="kb-carousel__right">
              <i class="material-icons">keyboard_arrow_right</i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="kb-card__footer kb-row">
      <div class="kb-col kb-col--50">
        <p class="kb-card__support-text">
          Total Price
        </p>
